Generic single-database configuration with an async dbapi.

Migration Naming Convention
---------------------------
New migrations should follow a consistent naming pattern:
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "<NNN>_short_description"

Where <NNN> is the next sequential number (e.g., 012_add_avatar_column).
This keeps migrations easy to identify in chronological order.

Existing migrations with inconsistent names should NOT be renamed,
as Alembic tracks them by revision hash, not filename.
